      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $A,B \\in \\mathcal{M}_n(\\R)$ telles que $AB = BA$.\n    Montrer que $\\det(A^2 + B^2) \\ge 0$.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A,B \\in \\mathcal{M}_n(\\R)\\)</span> telles que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(AB = BA\\)</span>. Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\det(A^2 + B^2) \\ge 0\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "f5ac0035-be43-448d-af75-042dc81f674c",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Chercher $A,B$ ne commutant pas telles que $\\det(A^2 + B^2) < 0$.",
        "html": "<p>Chercher <span class=\"math inline\">\\(A,B\\)</span> ne commutant pas telles que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\det(A^2 + B^2) &lt; 0\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
