      "value": {
        "latex": "$A = \\begin{pmatrix} 1        &\\lambda \\cr\n                            \\lambda  &1       \\cr \\end{pmatrix}$,\\quad\n             $B = \\begin{pmatrix} 0        &\\lambda \\cr\n                            -\\lambda &0       \\cr \\end{pmatrix}$,\\quad\n             $|\\lambda| > \\frac 12$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(A = \\begin{pmatrix} 1        &amp;\\lambda \\cr\n                            \\lambda  &amp;1       \\cr \\end{pmatrix}\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(B = \\begin{pmatrix} 0        &amp;\\lambda \\cr\n                            -\\lambda &amp;0       \\cr \\end{pmatrix}\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(|\\lambda| &gt; \\frac 12\\)</span>.</p>\n"
